  "title": "Lymphatic drainage of the face",
  "body_html": "<div>Lymph drainage from the face involves three key lymph node groups<br /><br /><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class = \"tlarge table table-striped table-bordered\"  data-role=\"table\" id=\"tableid1\" ><thead><tr><th>Area drained</th><th>Lymph node</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Forehead</td><td>Submandibular (central forehead)<br />Preauricular & parotid (temple and lateral forehead)</td></tr><tr><td>Anterior portion of face<br />Inferomedial periorbital area (inc medial lower eyelid)<br />External nose<br />Nasolabial area<br />Upper lip<br />Lower lip (lateral)</td><td>Submandibular</td></tr><tr><td>Lateral portion of face<br />Lateral cheek and temporal region<br />Upper eyelid<br />Lateral lower eyelid</td><td>Preauricular & Parotid</td></tr><tr><td>Lower lip (central)</td><td>Submental</td></tr><tr><td>Chin</td><td>Submental</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><I>Images illustrating lymph drainage from the eyelid and lips</I><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti117b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti117.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></div><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti118b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti118.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">1</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Anatomy</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Head & neck</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nLymph drainage from the face involves three key lymph node groups<br /><br /><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class = \"tlarge table table-striped table-bordered\"  data-role=\"table\" id=\"tableid1\" ><thead><tr><th>Area drained</th><th>Lymph node</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Forehead</td><td>Submandibular (central forehead)<br />Preauricular & parotid (temple and lateral forehead)</td></tr><tr><td>Anterior portion of face<br />Inferomedial periorbital area (inc medial lower eyelid)<br />External nose<br />Nasolabial area<br />Upper lip<br />Lower lip (lateral)</td><td>Submandibular</td></tr><tr><td>Lateral portion of face<br />Lateral cheek and temporal region<br />Upper eyelid<br />Lateral lower eyelid</td><td>Preauricular & Parotid</td></tr><tr><td>Lower lip (central)</td><td>Submental</td></tr><tr><td>Chin</td><td>Submental</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><I>Images illustrating lymph drainage from the eyelid and lips</I><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti117b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti117.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></div><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti118b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/fti118.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'></td><td align='right'></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br></div>",
